<body>
    <h1>Spicy Pork Stir Fry</h1>

    <img src="../pictures/stirfry.jpg" alt="picture of stirfry">

    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>One lb ground pork</li>
            <li>60 ML Soy Sauce</li>
            <li>4 tbsp Ginger</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Garlic</li>
            <li>1 shallot</li>
            <li>1 lime</li>
            <li>1.5 cups green beans<li>
        </ul>
    

    <h3>Steps</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>heat green beans in pan, add salt as needed</li>
            <li>remove green beans, add garlic, shallot, ginger, stir rapidly</li>
            <li>add ground pork, break up and brown in pan</li>
            <li>add zest of lime, soy sauce and brown sugar, stir rapidly</li>
            <li>serve over rice or noodles with sriracha and a spritz of lime</li>
            <li>Enjoy!</li>
        </ol>
    

